      <title>拉加德：不是“预先承诺特定的利率路径”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/lagarde-not-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德周四在法兰克福举行的新闻发布会上讨论最新利率决定时表示，央行并未“预先承诺”利率路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/lagarde-not-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-video</guid>
